data.description: Wonderful North Point home with tons of upgrades. There are 3 bedrooms 2 baths and extra room that could be used as office, bedroom, or second living area.  Open floor plan with a great kitchen with eating area and then formal dining area.  Beautiful entry way.  Master is large with nice bathroom.  The owner had a 2 car carport added to the home that has brick and is an extension of the roof with lots of storage above it plus it has the regular 2 car garage.  Back yard is very nice for entertaining.  Storage building in the back.
